,    {"who": "Edith Zierer", "start": "1122.890","u": "And we studied English, but now we can&#39;t study three languages at once."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1126.814","u": "Yes, and one shouldn&#39;t."},    {"who": "Edith Zierer", "start": "1128.178","u": "So we study two languages, geography, history, and . . ."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1133.611","u": ". . . et cetera."},    {"who": "Edith Zierer", "start": "1134.414","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1135.006x","u": "Do you work? Do you help with the chores?"},    {"who": "Edith Zierer", "start": "1136.956","u": "Yes, every child helps here. Every week . . . every week a different child has duty in the kitchen, no? She works. Or a duty [?] in the house, in the garden."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1147.507","u": "And who attends [takes care of] the little children?"},    {"who": "Edith Zierer", "start": "1149.771","u": "There are such two women, no?"},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1153.381","u": "Two women take care of the small children."},    {"who": "Edith Zierer", "start": "1154.878","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1155.409","u": "Do you have to help out with it?"},    {"who": "Edith Zierer", "start": "1157.220","u": "No, not now any more."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1158.669","u": "Nu, and what do you think will become of you?"},    {"who": "Edith Zierer", "start": "1163.184","u": "I don&#39;t know."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1164.150","u": "Oh. [Pause.] What do you want to learn? What would you like to study? What do you like to learn?"},    {"who": "Edith Zierer", "start": "1172.287","u": "I want to study? [Pause.]"},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1174.840","u": "Yes."},    {"who": "Edith Zierer", "start": "1176.319","u": "I don&#39;t know [?]."},    {"who": "David Boder", "start": "1178.915","u": "How much schooling did you have?"},    {"who": "Edith Zierer", "start": "1180.865","u": "Schooling? I have 